snippet.title: SCARLET NEXUS – Announcement Trailer | Xbox Series X
snippet.description:
In a far distant future, humanity’s last hope falls into the hands of an elite group of psionic soldiers, who battle an invincible threat known as, #Others.

Unravel the mysteries of a #BrainPunk future caught between technology and psychic abilities in, #SCARLETNEXUS Follow the link for more info: bandainam.co/SNX-info

Follow SCARLET NEXUS: 
Instagram: https://instagram.com/scarletnexusofficial
Twitter: https://twitter.com/scarlet_nexus
